_text = "This was my favourite photo I took. I took this inside a car as we sped past this landscape. It was on our way to Fernie, right before the mountains begin.\n\nI saw this other vehicle driving towards the windmills and just knew I had to capture this moment.\n\nI often fear that if I didn't take this photo, this memory would have been forever lost.\n\nHowever, as we continued down the road I questioned if we should turn around or go back to the mountains.\n\nReturn home (Left) or Continue on (Right)"
//this is only for left or right choice

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, Monitor, MonitorNo, MonitorYes, BasketballCourtMemory, MistyWoodsMemory, false)
